{"tid":2239271,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"任志強被重判丨官媒披露犯案細節 貪污5,700萬 兒子顧問費佔4,200萬　","createTime":"2020-10-11T18:55:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T02:20:20.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e5693949ed6e596c9044cbae04662274e749ea85","tid":2239271,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T18:55:23.000Z","msg":"華遠集團前董事長任志強被指涉及貪污、受賄、挪用公款、國有公司人員濫用職權等罪，9月下旬遭北京人民法院重判18年有期徒刑。《人民日报》海外版官方微博「俠客島」周日（11日）發文，詳述任志強貪污濫權情況，指他在華遠貪污的近半億人民幣，大部份用來支付兒子的「財務顧問費」。<br />\n<br />\n文章指，任志強在華遠集團一人獨大，利用職務便利，貪污公款、收受賄賂、挪用公款的真面目，令國企蒙重大損失，涉款逾2.2億元人民幣（下同，約2.54億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n文章首先指，任志強在華遠擔當「一把手」近20年，以不同手法貪污公款4,974萬餘元（約5,741萬港元），其中3,640萬元（約4,201萬港元）是支付給其兒子的「財務顧問費」。<br />\n<br />\n除了夥同兒子等人非法佔有巨額公款之外，任志強將任職期間的1,334萬元（約1,540萬港元）超限薪酬在公司掛賬，於退休後領取的行為，也被法院認定為貪污罪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201012/FUIBRKAJIVBMLDIBAZ3Q4DY6XY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201012%2FFUIBRKAJIVBMLDIBAZ3Q4DY6XY%2F&d=aqHBcmSoErOqRK7CI6xlBbvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=2f1fefca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201012%2FFUIBRKAJIVBMLDIBAZ3Q4DY6XY%2F&h=13188502\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201012/FUIBRKAJIVBMLDIBAZ3Q4DY6XY/</a>"},{"pid":"67f084c191e0428a639b6fd5c0c846f190fb4bc4","tid":2239271,"uid":153811,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T18:57:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d926590697ac04379f1b4369b98d718b7468792f","tid":2239271,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T18:59:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\